sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>HTTPS Reencrypt
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant WfCtrl as Workflow Controller<br/>(Argo)
    participant PipelinePod as Pipeline Pod
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant MLMD as Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Envoy as Metadata Envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC-Web
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>9000/TCP or 443/TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution
        User->>Route: POST pipeline run request
        Route->>KRBP: HTTPS (reencrypt TLS)
        KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(dspa resource check)
        KRBP->>API: Proxy to 8888/TCP<br/>(authed request)
        API->>MariaDB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>3306/TCP MySQL<br/>TLS (conditional)<br/>Username/Password
        API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ (external)<br/>Access Key/Secret Key
        API->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>WfCtrl: Workflow CR event
        WfCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pipeline Pod<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>PipelinePod: Pod scheduled
        PipelinePod->>API: Report status<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS (conditional)<br/>Projected SA token (pipelines.kubeflow.org)
        PipelinePod->>MLMD: Record artifacts/executions<br/>8080/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (conditional)
        PA->>API: Sync workflow status<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS (conditional)<br/>Projected SA token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,MariaDB: Flow 2: MLMD Access
        User->>Route: Access ML Metadata
        Route->>KRBP: HTTPS (reencrypt TLS)
        KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(dspa resource check)
        KRBP->>Envoy: Proxy to 9090/TCP
        Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC-Web → gRPC<br/>8080/TCP<br/>TLS (conditional)
        MLMD->>MariaDB: Query lineage data<br/>3306/TCP MySQL<br/>TLS (conditional)<br/>Username/Password
        MariaDB-->>MLMD: Lineage results
        MLMD-->>Envoy: gRPC response
        Envoy-->>KRBP: gRPC-Web response
        KRBP-->>Route: HTTPS response
        Route-->>User: ML Metadata results
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Managed Pipeline Injection
        Note right of API: Operator inspects OCI manifest<br/>validates against registry allowlist
        PipelinePod->>S3: Init container pulls<br/>pipeline image from OCI registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Registry credentials
        S3-->>PipelinePod: Pipeline definition artifacts
        Note right of PipelinePod: Extracts to shared<br/>emptyDir volume
        PipelinePod->>API: API server reads<br/>pipeline definitions from<br/>shared emptyDir mount
    end
